  "title": "Understanding 'Gu Gu Ga Ga': Definition and Importance",
  "lessonText": "In this section, we will explore the concept of 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' and its significance in our lives.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- **Definition**: 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' refers to the playful sounds and expressions often used by infants and young children.\n- **Importance**: These sounds are crucial for language development and emotional expression.\n- **Cultural Relevance**: Different cultures have unique interpretations and uses of 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' in early childhood.\n- **Developmental Role**: Engaging with 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' enhances bonding between caregivers and children."
